I downloaded this as screenshots and sample were good, its got cd1 and cd2 avi files, I can't open cd1, keep getting "file is corrupted", or " file is wrong format" cd2 is perfect audio and video, so "sharana" you can't always rely on samples or screenshots. My nearest cinema is 30 miles away and I live in the country, I don't have transport, am disabled, and I rely on "comments" made as i have a monthly download limit with my ISP. If anyone can get or has gotten cd1 open please let us know in a "comment" also the program that opened it, Thank You
moviemessenger, Hash Check this torrent. cd1 is good.

Thanks "sharana" I use BitComet for downloading and thought I had Hash Check enabled just checked it and I haven't, also being at bit of a newbie at this, I'm not to sure how to do it once the download is complete,any help would be most appreciated,Thanks in advance.

I took most of the day, but figured it out, Hash Checked cd1, only 99% of it had downloaded,done that, tried it out and its working now, perfect audio & video on both cd1 & cd2, thanks "sharana" for the info, it pays to have Hash Check enabled, also thanks to "changebg
